Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:00:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,2011年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一种病毒杀死了百分之九十九的人口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一个叫特雷沃古查迪的科学家 研制出疗法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,幸存的五百万人生活在布列尼亚城 地球最後的一座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,古查迪王国统治了四百年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,反叛分子出现挑战古查迪政权
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,2415年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有人称布列尼亚城为完美社会\NSome call Bregna the perfect society.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有人称它为人类文明的高峰\NSome call it the height of human civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但有些人知道并不是如此\NBut others know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,古查迪的人兴建布列尼亚城 确保我们的未来\NThe Goodchilds built Bregna to ensure us a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们建造了尼列高飞艇…\NThey built the Relical.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,提醒我们发生过的惨事\NA memorial to remind us of what we've survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们建造围墙保护我们\NThey built walls to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们告诉我们，外面世界已被 大自然重新掌管\NThey tell us that outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,nature has retaken the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但真正问题是在里面\NBut the real problems lie within.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有莫名的伤痛\NWe are haunted by sorrows we cannot name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,总有人失纵…\NPeople disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们的政府否认这些控罪\Nand our government denies these crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,古查迪政权保护我们 只要我们服从它\NThe Goodchild regime provides for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as we stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们用自由换取美丽的牢笼\NSo we trade freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,for a gilded cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但有些反叛分子不肯就范…\NBut there are rebels who refuse to make that trade,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们致力推翻一个禁制我们的政府…\Nwho fight to overthrow a government that silences us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,为失纵的人而战\Nwho fight, in the name of the disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们叫自己做摩根战士\NThey call themselves, the Monicans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我是其中一个\NI am one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,汉娜\NHandler.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,依昂\NAeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有一项任务\NWe have an assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想你去破坏古查迪的 中央监察系统\NWe want you to sabotage Goodchild's central surveillance facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,系统会发现你的入侵，但我们会 暂时切断他们的内部警钟\NYour entry will be noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but we will briefly disrupt their interior alarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,监视系统是他们对付我们最厉害武器\NSurveillance is their greatest tool against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他们见到摩根战士 我们就会被捉\NAs long as Monicans can be seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we can be targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你去“弄瞎”他们\NWe need you to blind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,每个任务都有助推翻古查迪政权\NEach mission brings us closer to defeating the Goodchild regime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我女儿，你见过她吗？\NThis is my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她在两个月前失纵了\NHave you seen her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She disappeared two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,求你帮我，小姐 你有见过这女孩吗？\NHelp me, please, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她在两个月前失纵了\NShe disappeared two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,失眠？发恶梦？\NLosing sleep? Having bad dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,到我们的睡眠医疗中心，寻求辅助吧\NVisit our sleep center for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,失眠？发恶梦？到我们的睡眠…\NLosing sleep? Having bad dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,买东西给我吗，婉娜？\NVisit our sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shopping for me, Una?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道吗？今天是特别日子\NHaven't you heard? It's a special occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的姊姊终於来吃晚饭\NMy sister's finally coming to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我和克劳多斯都很期待呢\NClaudius and I are looking forward to tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,终於这一次，你将不会坐一会儿就走\NFor once, you'll be in the house long enough to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我约你在这里见\NThat's why I wanted to meet with you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,依昂\NAeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我今晚可能来不了，对不起\NI may not make it tonight, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不要生气\NDon't be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不是因为你不能来吃晚饭\NIt's not that you can't come to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,而是你要去做的事\NIt's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前常常想像你会加入我们\NYou know, I used to imagine you'd come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们解决问题的方法不同\NWe have different ways of solving problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，你逃避它\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎样可以逃避它？\NYou ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I possibly ignore them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，她是我女儿\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我见到问题，我感觉到\NI see the problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She disapear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但我尝试找出它的好处\NAnd I'm trying to make something good out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-找一种生活 -这算一种什麽生活？\NA life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of life is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也有美好的东西\NThere are good things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就是有你\NThere's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-我有一个惊喜给你 -说给我知\NSo I have a surprise for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚\NTonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要小心\NSo be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要安全回来\NAnd come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,失眠？发恶梦？\NLosing sleep? Having bad dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,到我们的睡眠医疗中心，寻求辅助吧\NVisit our sleep center for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,失眠？发恶梦？\NLosing sleep? Having bad dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,到我们的睡眠医疗中心，寻求辅助吧\NVisit our sleep center for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怀疑是摩根战士集团 一共有三个目标\NPossible Monican consort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Three subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要求身份辨认\NIdentification requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怀疑是摩根战士活动\NPossible Monican activity suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不是因为你不能来吃晚饭\NIt's not that you can't come to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,而是你要去做的事\NIt's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前常常想像你会加入我们\NYou know, I used to imagine you'd come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们解决问题的方法不同\NI think we have different ways of solving problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,现实如此，但我尝试…\NThis is the way things are and I'm trying,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,找出它的好处，找一种生活\Nto make something good out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Identification requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你早了，克劳多斯\NYou're early, Claudius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们无处不在\NBut they're everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要保护你\NWe need to protect you from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是古查迪主席对付 摩根战士的方法\NThis is how Chairman Goodchild deals with Monicans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但她不是…\NShe wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是摩根战士\NShe wasn't a Monican.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,曾几何时，我有家人\NI had a family once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我有生活\NI had a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我只有一个任务\NNow all I have is a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,婉娜\NUna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,依昂\NAeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,依昂、婉娜\NAeon, Una.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,依昂\NAeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,安全回来\NUna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在想见你\NShe will see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,汉娜\NHandler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,依昂\NAeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有个任务\NWe have an assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一个你一直等着的任务\NOne you've been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,古查迪\NGoodchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们截查了些资料，它可以让我们 进入他的保护系统\NWe've intercepted information that will allow us to penetrate his security.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想你杀了他\NWe want you to eliminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该早点派我去\NYou should've sent me in earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-那只是会送死 -我不会有事\NThat would've been suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,忍耐点，依昂\NNot for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们花了一年时间才得到那资料\NPatience, Aeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It has taken a year to get the information we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你想替婉娜报仇\NI know you want to do this for Una.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但你要记住，你有更重要的使命\NBut you must remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,this is larger than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是唯一被无辜杀害的人\NShe's not the only innocent person who's been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的时机到了\NThis is our moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在的力量最强\NWe have never been stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，人们很恐惧…\NPeople are frightened yes but,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但只要我们引领他们…\Nif we show them the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,当他死後，他们就会支持我们\Nthey will rise behind us when he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我已准备好\NI'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,明天，古查迪会向议会发表演说\NTomorrow, Goodchild will be preparing his address to the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要到达政府区域，你要穿过边境花园\NTo reach the government zone, you will need to cross the frontier garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,当你穿过花园，你要全速赶往 斯坦迪楼\NOnce you are through the garden, you must move quickly to the Citadel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,为了混淆入侵者，地底建有多条隧道\NThe underground interior has been built to be confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已植入一条路线给你，跟着它\NWe've implanted a route for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我想史多娜和我一起去\NI want Sithandra with me for the crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，到论坛去\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,主席古查迪会在那里\NGet to the Forum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where Chairman Goodchild will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,去到你自然知要怎做\NYou know what to do from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死他，你就大仇得报\NDo this and you will have your revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就会得到胜利\NAnd we will all have our victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哟，史多娜\NHello, Sithandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-仍然吓不到你 -你还未够班\NStill can't surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你的改善手术如何？\NHow are the modifications?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,很有用\NUseful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你也应该做\NYou should have it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢穿鞋\NI like my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,警告，这是平民区域边界，严禁前进\NWarning. End of civilian zone. Do not proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,警告，严禁前进\NWarning. Do not proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好没有？\NReady?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,几时都准备好\NAlways.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,警告，严禁前进\NWarning. Do not proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-史多娜 -不要停\NSithandra. Let's keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-明白那系统吗？ -完全明白\NWe understand these now? Completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我会小心不踩到草地\NI'd keep off the grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-下午4点20分会合 -我会等你\NRendez vous at 16:20.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意铲除摩根战士的政策\NI agree with the policy of targeting proven Monican threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但我怕我们去得太尽\NBut I'm afraid we're going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对他们不可留情\NWe can't go too far with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,用怀柔政策有好处\NThere are advantages to showing a degree of leniency.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以令他们有幻想，一个也不可以\NWe can't allow them the luxury of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,暴力不是唯一方法\NBrute force isn't the only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但它很有效\NIt's an effective one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,摩根战士越来越强，很快 暴力不足以对付他们\NThe Monicans are growing strong. Soon, force won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你想妥协？谈判？\NSo you want to compromise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要重新考虑政策\NNegotiate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The policy should be reconsidered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-投票决定 -政策不可用来辩论！\NPut to a vote. The policy is not up for debate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在就在辩论！\NI'm debating it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你再冷静些，朱路士\NI'd encourage you to look at this with a little more detachment, Giroux.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一定要客观\NHere, we must be impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会想触怒我吧？\NYou wouldn't want me to take your outburst personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,完毕\NThat is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,奥伦？\NOren?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始担心，奥伦你那恶劣的态度\NI'm getting worried about you, Oren. This edge you've taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那种态度帮不了我们\NDisplays like that aren't helpful to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想保护我们创造的一切 我不会为这道歉\NI believe in protecting what we've created. I won't apologize for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,它被创造的目的 是让我完成我的工作\NThis was created to allow me to do my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如你不能控制自己，我会无法完成\NI can't do that if you can't control yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-明白 -真的？\NUnderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-测试结果如何？ -全失败\NAnd what about the test results?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在早上之前帮我找新的测试小组\NFind me a new test group by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,或者我们应该放弃测试，特雷沃\NMaybe it's time to give up on the tests, Trevor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经找到解决方法，它很完美\NWe're living the solution already. This is perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-为何你不可接受它？ -看看人们发生的事\NWhy can't you just embrace it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what's happening to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道它的严重性\NYou know how desperate this has become.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可控制它，阻止它恶化\NIt can be contained.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘记这一切只是暂时性\NControlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're forgetting that this was all meant to be temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直这样说，但怎会是暂时性？\NWe've always said that, but why should it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是错的\NBecause it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,世事会变\NThings change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知你不会\NBut I know you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你很了解我\NYou know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做了多年兄弟\NI've been your brother a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得没错\NYou're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,特雷沃，你的演说\NTrevor, your speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,特雷沃…\NTrevor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一点用也没有\NUseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-说出目的地 -论坛\NState destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Forum.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.49,0:22:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,向前行\NProceed forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.70,0:22:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,向左行\NProceed left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们恐惧\NI know you have fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的哀伤动摇你们信念和耐性\NYou have sorrows that shake your belief and try your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在这一刻，我们必须团结一致…\NBut now more than ever, we must stand together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们当中有些人…\Nbecause there are those among us,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,会摧毁我们创造的一切\Nwho would tear down what we have built.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.35,0:23:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,摩根战士想离间我们\NThe Monicans seek to divide us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不可忘记自己是谁…\NWe must never forget who we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.19,0:23:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们生存在一个孤独的前哨站\Na lonely outpost, a tiny band.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.86,0:23:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的祖先曾经遍布地球\NWe're all that remains of a people that once covered the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要团结一起应付新挑战\NWe must adapt together to these new challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,记住我们面对过的事、捱过的灾难\NRemember what we have faced,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.11,0:23:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,what we have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会捱过\NWe will adapt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们总会捱过\NWe have always adapted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们的特质\NIt's the fabric of who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.67,0:23:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳\NKatherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是你\NIt's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.80,0:24:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳\NKatherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.55,0:25:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在外面等\NWait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.17,0:25:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,依昂\NAeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.17,0:25:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前不是这样叫我\NYou called me by another name earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.37,0:25:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，而你没杀我\NI did, and you let me live.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.27,0:25:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,把枪还给我，我们再试试\NGive me my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.05,0:25:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll try it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.84,0:25:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,或者迟些吧\NMaybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.05,0:25:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麽名字？\NWhat was that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.78,0:25:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识我的，是吗？\NYou know me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.65,0:25:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.62,0:26:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道自己是谁吗？\NDo you know who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.26,0:26:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-我知道我来的目的是杀你 -所以你在牢中\NI know I came here to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.02,0:26:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're in a cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.76,0:26:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但有某个原因令我们仍生存\NBut we're both still alive for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.94,0:26:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道是什麽…\NI don't know what this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.61,0:26:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但见到你真好\Nbut it's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.35,0:27:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,新丁\NAmateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.32,0:28:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真乖\NGood boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.12,0:28:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-依昂 -有点忙，史多娜\NAeon. Little busy, Sithandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.42,0:28:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了吗？\NIs it done?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.59,0:28:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要多些时间\NI need more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.59,0:28:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,关於他的资料可能有错\NOur information on him may be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.53,0:28:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白，我们要继续，我希望你…\NI don't understand this, we have to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.92,0:28:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不要质疑我，史多娜\NI hope you... Don't question me, Sithandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.80,0:29:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我很快会联络你\NI'll contact you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.10,0:29:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,伊昂，你知道这会有严重後果\NAeon, you know there will be consequences to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.24,0:29:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道自己在做什麽\NI know what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.85,0:29:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,简直荒谬\NThis is outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.08,0:29:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一个摩根战士避过我们所有的 防卫系统？\NOne Monican eluding all of our defenses?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.32,0:29:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,问题会尽快处理\NThe problem will be taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.82,0:29:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是特雷沃的安全观念\NThe problem is Trevor's concept of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.22,0:29:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要学习接受较传统的…\NHe needs to learn to accept more traditional...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.39,0:29:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要学习接受我们的意见\NHe needs to learn to accept our input.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.89,0:29:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个例子证明他只追求自己的目的 不理我们的想法\NAnother example of him pursuing his own agenda,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.06,0:29:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-我开始质疑他的目的 -为什麽？\Nno matter what we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.96,0:29:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beginning to question his agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.61,0:29:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那摩根战士想杀他，但他却留她活口\NMeaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.90,0:29:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monican tries to kill him and he lets her live?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.63,0:29:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这很奇怪\NAn unusual choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.67,0:29:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在她逃走了\NAnd now she's escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.24,0:29:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有人相信这是巧合吗？\NDoes anyone believe this is a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.01,0:29:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们真的认为我很想听…\NDo you really think that I'm a sympathetic ear
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.84,0:29:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们对特雷沃的不满吗？\Nfor your complaints about Trevor?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.18,0:29:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你们没有权质疑他的做法\NYou don't have the right to question what he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.08,0:29:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你要留心，奥伦\NYou must be concerned, Oren.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.15,0:29:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是正常做法\NThis is hardly routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.02,0:29:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我应该跟特雷沃谈谈\NI think I should talk with Trevor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.36,0:29:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而你们的言行就应谨慎点\NAnd I think all of you, should be more discreet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.93,0:29:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,伊那里？\NInari?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.13,0:30:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,影像恢复开始\NImage retrieval commencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.84,0:30:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什麽事？\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.34,0:30:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我的情报员强调这点\NMy sources were clear on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.01,0:30:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,依昂佛洛丝是最强的摩根战士\NAeon Flux is the best the Monicans have.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.24,0:30:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-她失败了 -以前从未试过\NShe failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.43,0:30:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.64,0:30:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我想做得乾手净脚\NI wanted this done cleanly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.51,0:30:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-我兄弟… -没有防范\NMy brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.62,0:30:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Will be vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.45,0:30:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,准备他的演说…\NPreparing his speech...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.95,0:30:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,明天下午1点…\NTomorrow, 1300.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.42,0:30:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,无论怎样也不会查到是你\NIt can't be traced to you, in any case.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.83,0:30:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那我安心了\NThat's comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.89,0:30:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做得天衣无缝\NWe did everything correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.50,0:30:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-她的确有机会下手 -但她停住了\NShe had her opportunity. And she stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.57,0:30:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为什麽？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.64,0:30:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不知道 -影像恢复进行中\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.52,0:30:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Image retrieval underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.04,0:30:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在要求另一个暗杀行动太危险\NIt'll be too risky to call another hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.44,0:30:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,摩根战士会怀疑被人利用\NThe Monicans may suspect they are being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.95,0:30:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,停\NStop.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.42,0:30:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,奥伦？\NOren?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.49,0:30:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.42,0:31:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\NThat's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.24,0:31:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,克劳多斯\NClaudius.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.67,0:31:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-为何你还在这里？ -事情不是你想像般简单\NWhy are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.08,0:31:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as simple as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.65,0:31:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,婉娜被杀，而你就继续帮凶手辨事？\NUna is murdered and you keep working for the people who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.85,0:31:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-我应该怎想？ -你不明白\NWhat should I be thinking? You don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.98,0:31:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白什麽？\NWhat don't I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.52,0:31:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们杀了她\NThey killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.62,0:31:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-而你仍然活着 -是你杀了她，依昂\NAnd you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.70,0:31:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed her, Aeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.69,0:31:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们以为她是摩根战士，所以她被杀\NThey thought she was a Monican, that's why she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.80,0:31:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-婉娜不应就这样死去 -她是我唯一所有\NUna's life was worth more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.41,0:31:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She was all I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.03,0:31:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\NYou're not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.61,0:31:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你究竟在这里做什麽，克劳多斯？\NWhat are you really doing here, Claudius?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.21,0:31:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,工作\NWorking.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.98,0:31:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在只剩这些\NIt's all that's left.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.68,0:31:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,工作，为特雷沃古查迪工作\NWorking.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.87,0:31:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For Trevor Goodchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.68,0:32:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前也恨他\NI blamed him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.42,0:32:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在我认为不是特雷沃的错\NBut now I don't think it was Trevor's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.79,0:32:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,特雷沃只想帮忙\NTrevor's trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.66,0:32:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有些不妥，伊昂，所有人\NSomething is wrong with us, Aeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.19,0:32:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.83,0:32:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你有发那些梦，是吧？\NYou have the dreams, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.36,0:32:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有些回忆根本不曾发生\NMemories of things that never happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.93,0:32:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,婉娜有过，我有过\NUna had them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.24,0:32:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在整个布列尼亚城都有发生\NI have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.50,0:32:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening all across Bregna.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.67,0:32:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-是什麽？ -不知道\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.86,0:32:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只告诉我们需要知道的\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.97,0:32:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They only tell us what we need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.54,0:32:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我的工作只是一个大型实验的 一小部份\NMy work is a small part of a larger experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.28,0:32:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-谁的实验？ -特雷沃的\NWhose experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.83,0:32:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在研究外面世界的情况\NTrevor's.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.48,0:32:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're studying what's growing outside the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.99,0:32:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,当他们治好工业病时，有些事发生了\NSomething happened when they cured the industrial disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.52,0:32:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有其他痛苦的事发生了\NSomething else sprung up in its place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.86,0:32:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有病\NWe're sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.13,0:32:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,而特雷沃尝试医好我们 我只知道这些\NAnd Trevor's trying to cure us. That's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.07,0:32:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,特雷沃想向我下毒\NTrevor tried to dope me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.04,0:32:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我里面是什麽\NTell me what's in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.08,0:33:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个口讯\NIt's a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.08,0:33:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,上面说什麽？\NWell, what does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.29,0:33:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你要喝它，这才有效\NYou have to drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.74,0:33:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.36,0:33:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱她\NI loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.13,0:33:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的\NYou know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.75,0:33:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,依昂\NAeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.15,0:33:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起让你受苦，但公开谈亦不安全\NI'm sorry for the pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.64,0:33:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not safe to talk in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.33,0:33:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,事情并不是表面那样\NNothing is as it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.86,0:33:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你是有机会的，为何你不下手？\NYou had your chance. Why did you hesitate?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.77,0:34:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道去那里找我\NYou know where to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.40,0:34:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-为何我会在这里？ -我要再见你\NWhy am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.27,0:34:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.71,0:34:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀死我的妹妹\NYou killed my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.07,0:34:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不知情\NI didn't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.88,0:34:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.28,0:34:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-这样就没罪了？ -不\NAnd that excuses you? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.61,0:34:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是战争，两边都有死伤\NBut this is a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.00,0:34:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,People on all sides die.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.85,0:34:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,她不应该死，她和这场战争无关\NShe shouldn't have. She had nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.02,0:34:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-每个人都有关 -她没有\NEveryone is involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.01,0:34:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.53,0:35:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不用武器也能杀你\NI don't need that to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.47,0:35:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但可以轻松些，不是吗？\NBut it would be easier, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.90,0:35:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当我看见你，一切也改变了\NEverything changed when I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.54,0:35:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识你，你也认识我\NI know you. And you know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.85,0:35:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为什麽我会认识你？为什麽？\NWhy do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.18,0:35:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.69,0:35:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为什麽你要回来？\NWhy did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.66,0:35:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想在我这里得到什麽？ -我想要什麽？\NWhat do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.09,0:35:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.83,0:35:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我要我的妹妹回来\NI want my sister back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.79,0:35:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我想记得做一个自由人的感觉\NI want to remember what it feels like to be a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.94,0:35:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,依昂\NAeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.61,0:35:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为何在你身边我会有这种感觉？\NWhy do I feel this way around you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.34,0:36:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳…\NKatherine...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.37,0:36:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识我\NYou know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.68,0:36:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你去杀了他\NI want you to eliminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.95,0:36:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,安全回来\NCome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.28,0:37:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是你所想的那种人，依昂\NI'm not who you think I am, Aeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.56,0:40:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有些东西遗漏了\NSomething is missing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.60,0:40:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已找出7A测试小组失败的原因\NWe identified the variables that compromised test group 7A.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.67,0:40:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,已安排上尼列高飞艇解决7B的问题 确保把他们隔离\NSchedule a Relical visit regarding 7B and make sure we isolate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.84,0:40:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是时间问题…\NIt's just a matter of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.34,0:40:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人迟早会发现并质疑这里 所发生的事\Nbefore people look up and question what's happening here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.71,0:40:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,找到你了\NFound you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.03,0:42:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很快会回复，主席\NNo permanent damage here, Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.04,0:42:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以离开\NYou may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.65,0:43:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她逃走了\NShe's escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.65,0:43:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,为何我不惊讶？\NWhy am I not surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.58,0:43:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我在图书馆找到她\NI found her in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.62,0:43:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-我想我伤了她，但… -你袭击她？\NI think I wounded her, but... You attacked her?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.32,0:43:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她是摩根派来的人，想杀死你\NShe's a Monican agent who tried to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.86,0:43:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我已有足够理由这样做\NI assumed it was obvious what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.96,0:43:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,菲亚，我要她活着，明白吗？\NFreya, I want her alive. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.27,0:43:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,奥伦知道吗？\NIs Oren aware of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.47,0:43:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到他\NI can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.04,0:43:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,保持紧密\NStay close.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.78,0:43:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不论特雷沃以前为我们做过什麽 他也不能免罪\NNo matter what Trevor's done for us in the past, he's not above reproach.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.48,0:43:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是叛国\NThis is treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.02,0:43:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,奥伦？\NOren?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.83,0:43:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,特雷沃跟我们相违背已有一段日子\NTrevor has been moving away from us for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.60,0:43:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里创建的一切比他重要\NWhat we've built here,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.20,0:43:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is larger than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.63,0:44:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没想过会变成这样，但我们 必须面对现实\NI never thought it would come to this, but we have to face the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.11,0:44:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他选择了那个摩根战士，而他知道 那有什麽後果\NHe chose that Monican and he knew what that would mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.58,0:44:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他必须被废除主席一职\NHe must be removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.15,0:44:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,而奥伦就是继任人\NAnd Oren is next in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.28,0:44:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗？\NIsn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.52,0:44:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.96,0:44:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那麽，就这样决定\NIt's done, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.06,0:44:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,主席先生\NMr. Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.33,0:44:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,特雷沃背叛了我们\NTrevor has betrayed all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.07,0:44:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他是罪犯\NHe's a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.90,0:44:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要杀了他\NWe'll treat him as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.04,0:44:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,7A测试小组\NTest group 7A.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.88,0:44:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,已安排上尼列高飞艇解决7B的问题 确保把他们隔离\NSchedule a Relical visit regarding 7B and make sure we isolate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.95,0:44:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是时间问题…\NIt's just a matter of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.38,0:44:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人迟早会发现和质疑这里 所发生的事\Nbefore people look up and question what's happening here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.85,0:44:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,回顾7B测试小组对象的进展…\NReview progress of subjects from test group 7B,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.59,0:44:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,桑德林威吾士、葛丽泰沙克 婉娜佛洛丝\NSandrin Veems, Greta Salk, Una Flux.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.36,0:45:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,已安排上尼列高飞艇取回新数据\NSchedule a Relical visit to retrieve new data.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.47,0:45:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,8.26、7.19\N8.26, 7.19.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.24,0:45:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,葛丽泰沙克、婉娜佛洛丝\NGreta Salk, Una Flux.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.57,0:45:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,已安排上尼列高飞艇取回新数据\NSchedule a Relical visit to retrieve new data.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.64,0:45:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,8.26、7.19\N8.26, 7.19.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.61,0:45:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,从尼列高飞艇的5.88分子链中 收集额外样本\NCollect additional samples from Relical strands 5.88.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.72,0:45:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀他时一定是很轻手\NYou're certainly killing him kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.03,0:45:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,情况有变\NThe situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.20,0:45:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我们的命令\NOur orders haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.67,0:45:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再服从命令\NI'm not following orders anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.00,0:45:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,为何你要这样做，依昂？\NWhy are you doing this, Aeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.04,0:45:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一切变得复杂\NEverything has become more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.21,0:45:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不，很简单\NNo, it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.41,0:45:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,婉娜的死或许不关特雷沃事\NTrevor may not be responsible for Una's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.51,0:45:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-特雷沃？ -我尝试找出凶手\NTrevor?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.55,0:45:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to find out who is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.51,0:45:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你的任务是杀死古查迪 既然你不能或不会的话，那麽…\NYour mission was to kill Goodchild,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.81,0:45:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can't or won't do that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.62,0:46:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,把武器给我，穿过边境回去\NGive me your weapon and return across the frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.19,0:46:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-我没有教你要为自己着想吗？ -你教了我更多的东西\NDidn't I teach you to think for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.63,0:46:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me a lot more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.53,0:46:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托！\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.20,0:46:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如逼不得已我唯有伤你\NI can hurt you if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.14,0:46:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有感到不妥吗？\NDon't you feel something wrong inside you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.07,0:46:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,史多娜，我…\NSithandra I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.61,0:46:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我是谁\NI don't know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.48,0:46:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你也有这感觉，是吗？\NYou feel it too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.09,0:46:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我去\NCome with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.66,0:46:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起完成任务\NWe'll finish the mission together.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.93,0:46:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我办不到\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.11,0:48:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这种玩意本是很好玩的\NThis sort of thing used to be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.01,0:48:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在该怎处置你？\NNow what do I do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.35,0:48:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳\NKatherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.56,0:48:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,回来\NCome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.49,0:50:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,07.4.872\N07.4.872.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.47,0:50:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,知道，回到数据流\NNoted. Returned to stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.67,0:50:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,热尔格彼臣\NGregor Plitzen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.57,0:50:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,70.5.872\N70.5.872.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.65,0:50:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,知道，回到数据流\NNoted. Returned to stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.85,0:50:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,淑姬丹拿利\NSuki Denali.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.32,0:51:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,02.4.875\N02.4.875.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.36,0:51:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,知道，回到数据流\NNoted. Returned to stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.73,0:51:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来\NWelcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.91,0:51:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,婉娜佛洛丝\NUna Flux.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.94,0:51:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,32.4.870\N32.4.870.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.08,0:51:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,已收集\NCollected.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.48,0:52:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,成功分配成沙夏比鲁\NSuccessfully reassigned as Sasha Prillo.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.32,0:52:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,重覆\NRepeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.62,0:52:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,婉娜佛洛丝，分配成沙夏比鲁\NUna Flux. Reassigned as Sasha Prillo.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.53,0:52:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沙夏比鲁，地址\NSasha Prillo. Address.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.37,0:52:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,沙夏比鲁，地址\NSasha Prillo.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.73,0:52:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Address.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.30,0:52:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,汉娜\NHandler.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.60,0:52:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,史多娜\NSithandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.31,0:52:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,古查迪还活着\NGoodchild is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.51,0:53:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,伊昂失手了？\NAeon failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.54,0:53:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她不杀他\NShe let him live.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.95,0:53:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们之间有某种关系\NThere's something between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.32,0:53:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,某种私人关系\NSomething personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.92,0:53:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,解释\NExplain.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.62,0:53:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她拒绝执行任务\NShe abandoned the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.42,0:53:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我尝试阻止她，但她袭击我 留我在这里\NI tried to stop her,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.82,0:53:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and she attacked me and left me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.66,0:53:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里安全吗？\NAre you secure where you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.33,0:53:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也算安全\NFairly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.63,0:53:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,帮手将会来到\NHelp is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.57,0:53:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,依昂佛洛丝现在已成为逃亡者\NAeon Flux is now considered a fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.10,0:53:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她已作出反抗，必须当成危险人物\NShe has betrayed the resistance and must be considered a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.81,0:53:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,现在她和古查迪结盟，已站在他那边\NShe has aligned herself with Goodchild and is with him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.48,0:53:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须速战速决\NWe must move quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.48,0:53:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你要杀了她\NYou will eliminate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.98,0:53:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死她，然後完成她的任务\NKill her and then complete her mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.19,0:53:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,史多娜，向他们显示你所在\NSithandra, show them where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.76,0:53:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看见吗？\NDo you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.40,0:54:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-看见 -看见\NYes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.34,0:54:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看见\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.40,0:54:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了她，再由那里出发\NExtricate her and proceed from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.15,0:54:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,特雷沃？\NTrevor?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.60,0:54:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是她\NIt's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.53,0:54:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.00,0:54:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-她来过 -她在找什麽？\NShe was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.29,0:54:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What was she looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.54,0:54:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她妹妹\NHer sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.81,0:54:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,婉娜\NUna.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.22,0:54:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,婉娜佛洛丝\NUna Flux.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.96,0:55:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,下一页\NScroll down.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.90,0:55:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,7B测试小组的成员\NMember of test group 7B.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.43,0:55:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要7B的所有成员\NShow me all of 7B.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.34,0:55:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,桑德林威吾士\NSandrin Veems.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.57,0:55:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,7B成员\NMember of 7B.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.31,0:55:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,死於警方行动\NKilled in police action.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.78,0:55:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪里？\NWhere is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.08,0:55:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,葛丽泰沙克\NGreta Salk.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.95,0:55:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,7B成员\NMember of 7B.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.85,0:55:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,死於警方行动\NKilled in police action.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.06,0:55:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没人\NThere's nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.26,0:55:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,卡蜜拉艾狄\NCamille Abdi.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.43,0:55:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,7B成员\NMember of 7B.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.50,0:55:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,死於警方行动\NKilled in police action.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.94,0:55:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,婉娜佛洛丝\NUna Flux.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.64,0:55:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,7B成员\NMember of 7B.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.95,0:55:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,死於警方行动\NKilled in police action.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.53,0:56:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谁干的？\NWho did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.06,0:56:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所有行动由副主席奥伦古查迪授权\NAll actions authorized by Adjunct Chairman Oren Goodchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.64,0:56:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,菲亚，去我的实验室，找出 7B小组的笔记\NFreya, go to my lab, find the notes
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.09,0:56:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你要找个安全地方避避，他们作反\Nfrom group 7B.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.27,0:56:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to get to a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.73,0:56:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-两小时之後在那里见 -你要去哪里？\NThey're moving against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.21,0:56:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet me there in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.17,0:56:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要早过他们找到她 -特雷沃…\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.75,0:56:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to find her before they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.34,0:56:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,菲亚，在实验室见\NTrevor...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.32,0:56:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Freya, I'll see you at the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.42,0:56:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你要小心\NTake care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.23,0:56:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,婉娜\NUna.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.53,0:56:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是对的\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.87,0:56:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-求你不要伤害我的婴孩 -她很安全\NPlease don't hurt my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.22,0:56:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.78,0:56:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你复制她？\NYou cloned her?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.14,0:56:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我复制所有人\NI cloned everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.25,0:57:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们医治工业病时发生并发症\NThere was a complication when we cured the industrial disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.79,0:57:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,疫苗有意外的副作用\NThe vaccine had an unintended side effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.59,0:57:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不育\NSterility.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.69,0:57:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们人类只能再活一代\NOnly one more generation of our species could survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.10,0:57:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个绝望时刻\NIt was a desperate time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.70,0:57:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的责任…\NIt's our responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.17,0:57:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,复制技术从没在人类身上成功过\NCloning had never been used on humans successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.31,0:57:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们成功了\NBut we succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.28,0:57:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，当一个人死了，我们会将 他们的基因循环再用\NNow, when a person dies, their DNA is recycled.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.42,0:57:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我和奥伦兴建了尼列高飞艇 来贮存基因…\NOren and I built the Relical to store the DNA,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.52,0:57:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,掩饰复制过程\Nand conceal the cloning process.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.89,0:57:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,保管人寻找一对适合的夫妇…\NThe Keeper finds a suitable couple...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.19,0:57:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,利用食品添加济，我们造成 化学性怀孕\Nand using food additives, we induce a chemical pregnancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.57,0:57:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,当那个女人走来检查，我们就植入 复制了的胚胎\NWhen the woman comes in for an exam, we implant a cloned embryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.94,0:57:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,之後，一切自然地发生\NFrom there, things happen naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.61,0:58:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,九个月後，一个死了的市民重生\NIn nine months, a citizen who died is reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.81,0:58:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我和奥伦已复制了自己7代…\NFor seven generations, Oren and I have cloned ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.35,0:58:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,教自己，在我们所有人 仍生存的同时…\Ntaught ourselves, so that I could keep trying to find a cure...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.16,0:58:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以继续尝试寻找医治方法\Nwhile we all live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.86,0:58:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们？\NThat's what we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.80,0:58:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,复制品？\NCopies?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.17,0:58:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不只如此\NWe're more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.97,0:58:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是暂时\NIt wasn't supposed to be permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.45,0:58:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直试着寻找方法医治不育\NI've been trying to cure the infertility.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.55,0:58:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,婉娜是我其中一个测试对象\NUna was part of one of my test groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.82,0:58:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,奥伦骗了我\NOren lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.69,0:58:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他说她的测试也像其他人一样失败了\NHe told me her test had failed like the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.46,0:58:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但实情是她怀孕了\NBut she had become pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.87,0:58:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他杀死所有测试对象\NHe killed all of the subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.04,0:59:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,包括你妹妹\NYour sister included.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.47,0:59:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她怀了孕，所以他要杀死他\NHe killed her because she was pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.18,0:59:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,婉娜不知道…\NUna didn't know it but...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.48,0:59:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,她的婴儿会是400年来其中一个新生儿\Nher baby would've been one of the first new children in 400 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.89,0:59:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,奥伦变了\NOren's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.96,0:59:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他不想回到以前，他不想找到疗方\NHe doesn't want to go back. He doesn't want a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.13,0:59:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他想得到永生\NHe wants to live forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.54,0:59:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在你帮那摩根战士时，应已预料 有此结果\NYou must've been expecting this after helping that Monican.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.71,0:59:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你对特雷沃的忠诚已帮不了你\NYour loyalty to Trevor can't protect you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.98,0:59:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我是对一些更伟大的事忠诚\NI'm loyal to something deeper than any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.02,0:59:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白你和特雷沃这种人\NI don't understand people like you and Trevor.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.69,0:59:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的感性、对过去的执着…\NYour sentimentality, your devotion to the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.72,1:00:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对已过去的事的执着\Nto things that are gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.69,1:00:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没有这些，我不能活下去\NI couldn't live without those things.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.00,1:00:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎能做到的？\NHow can you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.58,1:00:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沙夏\NSasha.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.22,1:00:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要走了，奥伦很快会找到我们\NWe should go. It won't take long for Oren to find us.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.89,1:00:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她长大後会很难教\NShe's gonna be a handful.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.80,1:00:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,走，他们不是要对付你们\NGo. They don't want you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.43,1:00:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,走！\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.51,1:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,扒低！\NDown!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.13,1:04:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不，你不可以晕倒\NNo. You need to stay conscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.61,1:04:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,请保持冷静\NPlease remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.21,1:04:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正遇到技术故障\NWe are experiencing a technical malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.78,1:04:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,请保持冷静\NPlease remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.39,1:04:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正遇到技术故障\NWe are experiencing a technical malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.82,1:04:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,请保持冷静\NPlease remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.33,1:04:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正遇到…\NWe are experiencing...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.97,1:04:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能去摩根战士的藏身处\NWe can't go to a Monican safe house.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.67,1:04:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已没有安全的地方\NNowhere's going to be safe for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.86,1:05:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要将子弹拿出\NWe need to get the bullets out.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.50,1:05:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还有哪里受伤吗？\NAre you hit anywhere else?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.71,1:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们之中有人想念你吗？\NDid any of them manage to miss you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.70,1:06:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能要走出围墙\NWe might have to go outside the wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.50,1:06:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.54,1:06:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,首先，我要结束它\NFirst, I have to end this.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.38,1:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去里面\NI need to go back in.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.44,1:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在婉娜的测试小组中 拿回我的笔记\NI have to get my notes from Una's test group.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.01,1:06:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,奥伦会找到实验室并破坏它 破坏我所做的一切\NOren will find the lab and destroy it,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.80,1:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,everything I've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.07,1:06:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所有军队应向他们的岗位报告…\NAll military units should report to their stations
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.70,1:06:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,等待进一步指示\Nand wait for further instructions.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.18,1:07:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这里谁人话事？\NWho's in charge here?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.38,1:07:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你们的帮肋\NWe need your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.85,1:07:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-上头命令，一见你便要开枪 -发生了政变\NWe have orders to shoot you on sight. There's been a coup.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.49,1:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的命令是来自不合法的政府\NYour orders are coming from an illegitimate government.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.36,1:07:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要动，先生！ -你的名字是？\NStay where you are, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.38,1:07:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.69,1:07:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-什麽？ -我想知你的名字\NSir?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.55,1:07:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know your name.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.43,1:07:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫奥德，基利奥德\NIt's Ord.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.98,1:07:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我已不能命令你，基利 但他们也不能\NGarret Ord.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.57,1:07:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't command you anymore, Garret.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.88,1:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But neither can they.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.74,1:07:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你已得到自由\NYou're free.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.97,1:07:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你要下决定\NYou need to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.58,1:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,射我们还是帮我们，但要快决定\NShoot us or help us, but do it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.72,1:07:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,中将？\NLieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.49,1:07:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎样可帮到你，古查迪主席？\NHow can I help you, Chairman Goodchild?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.47,1:07:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要武器，我们要回到斯坦迪楼\NWe need weapons. We need to get back into the Citadel.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.34,1:07:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,知道\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.68,1:08:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,注意，请回到家中等候进一步指示\NAttention. Please return to your home and wait for further instructions.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.75,1:08:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会经常提供最新消息\NYou will be updated frequently.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.55,1:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这是议会和奥伦古查迪主席的宣布\NThis is an announcement from the Council and Chairman Oren Goodchild.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.69,1:08:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,注意，请回到家中等候进一步指示\NAttention. Please return to your home and wait for further instructions.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.87,1:08:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们近了 -等等\NWe're getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.28,1:08:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.96,1:08:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,特雷沃\NTrevor.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.53,1:08:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫我的那个名字…\NThe name you called me...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.43,1:09:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳\NKatherine.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.00,1:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,它曾是我的名字\NThat was my name.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.17,1:09:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾是我的妻子\NYou were my wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.34,1:09:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾经一起生活，就像其他人一样\NWe had a life together, just like anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.85,1:09:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\NWait.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.22,1:09:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你要告诉我\NYou need to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.12,1:09:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我在疫症期间失去你，我无法 把你重生\NI lost you during the disease, and you couldn't be brought back.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.63,1:09:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,之後我生生死死了七次\NI've lived and died seven times since then.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.50,1:09:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但每次我都告诉自己有关你的事\NAnd each time I taught myself about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.97,1:09:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我仍保留的意念\NYou were an idea I kept alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.67,1:09:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一些我必须想像的东西\NSomething I had to imagine.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.94,1:09:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但当我见到你…\NBut when I saw you...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.58,1:09:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我的感觉是那麽真实\Nwhat I felt was real.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.08,1:09:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识你\NI knew you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.39,1:09:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你\NI remembered you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.62,1:10:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所拥有的已穿越死亡、穿越一切\NWhat we had then survived in us past death, past everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.83,1:10:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我在找你\NI was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.93,1:10:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我在等着\NI've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.20,1:10:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是不同的人\NWe were different people.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.00,1:10:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,以前是\NWe were.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.01,1:10:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人已死了\NThose people are gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.54,1:10:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但属於他们的某东西回来了\NBut something in them came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.11,1:10:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.96,1:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得了\NI remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.87,1:10:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,外面有动乱\NIt's chaos out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.74,1:10:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了反抗古查迪的政变\NThere's a coup against Goodchild.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.81,1:10:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,令我们易於潜入\NMade it easier to slip in.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.97,1:10:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你有方法找她吗？\NDid you bring a way to find her?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.41,1:10:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,只要她体内的药丸仍在 我们就能找到她\NAs long as there's a trace of the pill in her,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.56,1:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,we can track her.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.02,1:11:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.94,1:11:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,菲亚\NFreya.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.32,1:11:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没了\NIt's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.85,1:11:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我已医好它\NI had cured it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.62,1:11:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我已找到答案\NI'd found the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.02,1:11:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,全毁了\NIt's all gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.50,1:11:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要继续前进\NWe have to keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.34,1:11:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有一件事要做\NThere's still one more thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.34,1:12:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,已没有事要做，我们要离开这里\NThere's nothing left to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.92,1:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I need to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.15,1:12:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走出围墙，重新生活\NWe go outside the wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.88,1:12:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一件事要做，我要摧毁它\NWe'll find a way to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.48,1:12:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one more thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.42,1:12:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.82,1:12:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.43,1:12:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是办法，依昂\NThis isn't the answer, Aeon.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.19,1:12:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能担保能再找到疗法\NThere's no guarantee I can find the cure again.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.66,1:12:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-复制是我们生存的唯一希望 -这不足够\NThe cloning is all we have.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.32,1:12:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.23,1:12:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的精神崩裂，每次你令我们重生 情况更严重\NOur minds are unraveling and every time you bring us back it gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.00,1:12:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样做的话，我们就灭绝\NIf you do this, we end.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.41,1:12:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们注定要死亡\NWe're meant to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.71,1:12:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们的一切才有意义\NIt's what makes anything about us matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.71,1:12:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这样生存着是折磨\NLiving like this is torture.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.88,1:12:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是鬼魂\NWe're just ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.55,1:12:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为这样\NThat's not how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.46,1:12:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不是\NNot now.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.67,1:12:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要小心\NLet's be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.74,1:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我们的对手是谁\NYou know who we're up against.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.38,1:13:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-这个举动很无聊 -这是信念的考验\NThis is an empty gesture.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.94,1:13:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不是由你来决定的\NIt's a leap of faith.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.51,1:13:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not for you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.55,1:13:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,依昂，我不想再失去你\NAeon,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.34,1:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.49,1:13:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会\NYou don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.39,1:13:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你会找到疗法\NYou'll find the cure again.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.83,1:13:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,玩完了，特雷沃\NIt's over, Trevor.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.20,1:13:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,向南尖顶爬去\NMoving into position on the south spire.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.54,1:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,事情变得比你的疗法更麻烦\NIt goes so much deeper than your cure.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.68,1:13:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,其他女人自然怀孕…\NOther women have been getting pregnant naturally,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.45,1:13:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是在实验中\Noutside of your experiments.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.75,1:13:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还越来越多人\NMore and more of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.72,1:13:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们自我治癒\NThey healed themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.59,1:13:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-你都杀了她们？ -我必须阻止\NAnd you killed them, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.08,1:13:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.39,1:13:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了多少人？\NHow many?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.13,1:14:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,多少人，奥伦？\NHow many, Oren?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.10,1:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,已没关系，大自然到最後找到了出路\NIt doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.85,1:14:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nature's finally found a way.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.67,1:14:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-准备好 -准备好\NIn position. In position.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.54,1:14:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,目标锁定\NPosition acquired.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.24,1:14:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,过时的是大自然，不是我们\NNature's the one who's obsolete,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.69,1:14:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,not us.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.45,1:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎会不明白自己创造的美丽？ 我就明白\NHow can you not understand, the beauty of what you made, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.99,1:14:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,情况变得复杂\NSituation's getting complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.46,1:14:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉我她死了\NYou told me, she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.10,1:14:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已尽力\NThere was nothing that they could do.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.58,1:14:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我下令摧毁她的基因\NI ordered her DNA destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.28,1:14:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟她在一起时变得不一样，特雷沃\NYou were a different man with her, Trevor.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.78,1:14:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她会阻止你做应该做的事\NShe would've stopped you from doing what needed to be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.09,1:14:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-就像她现在阻止你一样 -不，奥伦\NLike she's stopping you now. No, Oren.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.09,1:14:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.46,1:15:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-随时可开火 -等候我的信号\NWaiting for the go. On my signal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.42,1:15:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界，我们的世界很美丽\NThis world, our world, is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.29,1:15:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,值得我们用任何代价去保存它\NWorth preserving at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.53,1:15:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,它不能长久，它已破裂\NIt can't last. It's falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.84,1:15:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,史多娜，给我们信号\NSithandra, give us the signal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.71,1:15:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-史多娜 -先杀死佛洛丝\NSithandra. Take Flux down first.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.18,1:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你错了，奥伦\NYou're wrong in this, Oren.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.38,1:15:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们嬴了死亡、嬴了大自然\NWe've beaten death,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.65,1:15:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,beaten nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.98,1:15:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已超越你\NWe've gone beyond you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.32,1:15:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我要摆脱你\NAnd now I need to be free of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.59,1:15:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\NWait.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.68,1:15:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,史多娜\NSithandra.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.28,1:15:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是你自己的选择，依昂，已太迟了\NYou chose this, Aeon.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.86,1:16:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我们每个人有多痛苦\NIt's too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.42,1:16:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how much we're all suffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.55,1:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我在尝试结束它，特雷沃也是\NI'm trying to end it and so is Trevor.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.56,1:16:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我永不会背叛你\NI would never betray you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.09,1:16:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我\NHelp me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.46,1:16:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,史多娜\NSithandra.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.96,1:16:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你仍了解我\NYou still know me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.73,1:16:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了她\NFinish it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.97,1:16:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以选择相信我\NYou can choose to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.88,1:16:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了她\NFinish it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.98,1:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，奥伦\NI'm sorry, Oren.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.81,1:16:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.98,1:16:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\NI am, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.09,1:16:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,命令有变，掩护依昂、掩护古查迪\NOrders have changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.34,1:16:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Cover Aeon. Cover Goodchild.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.86,1:17:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,古查迪受了伤\NGoodchild's been hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.64,1:17:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,佛洛丝往法院去了\NFlux is headed to the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.24,1:17:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护依昂\NCover Aeon.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.39,1:18:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,史多娜！\NSithandra!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.98,1:19:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,奥伦\NOren.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.88,1:20:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他们快来了\NThey're coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.56,1:20:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,依昂\NAeon.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.78,1:20:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在等着你的命令\NWe're waiting for your orders.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.40,1:20:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是他们一份子？\NYou're not part of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.42,1:21:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何，我们不是无政府主义者\NWhatever we are, we're not anarchists.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.42,1:21:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-一定要有规有矩 -谢谢\NThere have to be rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.76,1:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.99,1:21:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你\NYou're the one.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.29,1:21:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是你救了我\NYou saved me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.32,1:21:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.56,1:21:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我在那时起就认识你\NI knew you then.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.49,1:21:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这个已损坏，摧毁它\NThis one was corrupted.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.10,1:21:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你是重要人物\NDestroy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.66,1:21:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were important.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.23,1:21:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她的基因完好\NThe DNA is good.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.00,1:21:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,摧毁它\NDestroy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.28,1:22:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我要保护你\NI knew that I needed to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.61,1:22:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我将你的基因收藏在这里 让它呈休眠状态\NI kept your DNA hidden,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.10,1:22:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,here, dormant.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.35,1:22:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我等到现在才把你复制\NI've waited until now, to bring you back.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.39,1:22:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为什麽？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.72,1:22:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你的力量会保留下来\NI knew that your strength would survive with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.96,1:22:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想如果我将你带回来，你可以 和特雷沃沟通\NI thought that if I brought you back,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.06,1:22:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you could reach Trevor.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.20,1:22:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都可以\NYou always could.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.04,1:22:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-我必须终止它 -没错\NI have to end it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.61,1:22:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.17,1:22:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,重新开始\NStart over.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.31,1:22:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那你会怎样？\NWhat about you?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.78,1:22:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我等这天已等了400年\NI've waited 400 years for this day.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.59,1:22:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我已累了\NI'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.39,1:22:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,活着，依昂\NStay alive, Aeon.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.17,1:22:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们需要你\NYou are needed.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.92,1:23:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,看！\NLook!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.72,1:25:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们可以向前行…\NNow we can move forward,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.69,1:25:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真真正正的活一次…\Nto live once,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.48,1:25:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,for real,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.30,1:25:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然後让位予其他可能做得更好的人\Nand then give way,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.27,1:25:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to people who might do it better.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.71,1:25:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,唏，凯瑟琳\NHey, Katherine.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.21,1:25:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我可再见你吗？\NWill I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.73,1:25:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只可活一次…\NTo live only once,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.77,1:25:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但却是充满希望\Nbut with hope.
